@startuml SD_16_CategoryManagement
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Category Management (Admin)
' FR-43: CRUD Categories + Toggle Active
' ============================================================

title **SD-16: Category Management\n(CRUD + Toggle Active)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #EFEBE9
    ParticipantBorderColor #4E342E
    ArrowColor #4E342E
}

actor "Admin" as Admin #Orchid
participant "Browser" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "AdminCategoryServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #EFEBE9
participant "CategoryService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "CategoryDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== View Category List ==

Admin -> Browser: Open Category Management
Browser -> Controller: GET /admin/categories
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getAllCategories()
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findAll()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT c.*,\nCOUNT(e.eventId) as eventCount\nFROM Categories c\nLEFT JOIN Events e ON ...\nGROUP BY c.categoryId\nORDER BY c.sortOrder
activate DB
DB --> DAO: List<Category>
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: categories
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: categories
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: Forward → admin/categories.jsp
deactivate Controller
Browser --> Admin: Category list:\nIcon, Name, Slug, Events Count,\nStatus, Actions

== Create New Category ==

Admin -> Browser: Click "Add Category"\n→ Fill form
Browser -> Controller: POST /admin/categories/create\n{name, description, icon,\nsortOrder}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: createCategory(data)
activate Service
Service -> Service: Auto-generate slug\nfrom name: "âm-nhạc" → "am-nhac"
Service -> DAO: create(category)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO Categories (\n  categoryId, name, slug,\n  description, icon,\n  sortOrder, isActive=1,\n  createdAt\n)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Created
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: category
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: category
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: Redirect + flash:\n"Category created successfully"
deactivate Controller
Browser --> Admin: ✅ Category added

== Toggle Category Active/Inactive ==

Admin -> Browser: Click toggle switch
Browser -> Controller: POST /admin/categories/toggle\n{categoryId}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: toggleActive(categoryId)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: toggleActive(categoryId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: UPDATE Categories SET\nisActive = CASE WHEN isActive=1\n  THEN 0 ELSE 1 END\nWHERE categoryId = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Updated
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: OK
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: OK
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: Redirect + flash:\n"Category status updated"
deactivate Controller
Browser --> Admin: ✅ Status toggled

@enduml
